          class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-dark lg:text-balance"
          data-aos="fade-right-sm"
          data-aos-delay="200"
        >
          Deep AI Expertise Across Industries
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-base font-medium text-light" data-aos="fade-right-sm" data-aos-delay="300">
          From machine learning algorithms to enterprise AI deployments, our team combines cutting-edge research with practical implementation experience to deliver transformative solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div 
        class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-2 gap-y-14 mt-12 lg:gap-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full" data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-dark">
              Machine Learning & Deep Learning
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-light">
              Advanced neural networks, computer vision, and natural language processing solutions that push the boundaries of what's possible.
            </p>
          </div>
          <ul role="list" class="mt-6 space-y-1 font-medium text-light">
            <li>
              <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  class="text-light icon icon-tabler-circle-check size-5"
                  slot="icon"
                >
                  <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path>
                  <path d="M5 12l5 5l10 -10"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm">Custom neural architectures</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  class="text-light icon icon-tabler-circle-check size-5"
                  slot="icon"
                >
                  <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path>
                  <path d="M5 12l5 5l10 -10"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm">Multi-modal AI systems</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full" data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-dark">
              Enterprise AI Strategy & Implementation
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-light">
              Comprehensive AI transformation strategies that align with business objectives and deliver measurable ROI.
            </p>
          </div>
          <ul role="list" class="mt-6 space-y-1 font-medium text-light">
            <li>
              <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  class="text-light icon icon-tabler-circle-check size-5"
                  slot="icon"
                >
                  <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path>
                  <path d="M5 12l5 5l10 -10"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm">AI readiness assessments</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  class="text-light icon icon-tabler-circle-check size-5"
                  slot="icon"
                >
                  <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path>
                  <path d="M5 12l5 5l10 -10"></path>
                </svg>
