              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-light">
                Our team has published numerous peer-reviewed papers and holds multiple patents in AI, contributing to the advancement of the field.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex overflow-hidden relative flex-col justify-between h-full rounded-2xl bg-theme-light"
            data-aos="fade-left-sm"
            data-aos-delay="200"
          >
            <div class="relative p-8">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-tertiary">Enterprise Scale</p>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium md:text-xl text-dark">
