            </h3>
          </dt>
          <dd class="p-8 border-t border-border">
            <p class="text-base font-medium text-light">
              Revolutionary recruitment technology that eliminates bias and matches candidates based on skills and potential, not demographics. Used by Fortune 500 companies to improve hiring diversity by 40%.
            </p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl shadow bg-secondary" data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-delay="200">
          <dt class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-white md:text-xl">
              Sully's Sandbox: AI Model Marketplace
            </h3>
          </dt>
          <dd class="p-8 border-t border-white/20">
            <p class="text-base font-medium text-white">
              A comprehensive platform for discovering, testing, and deploying AI models. Our curated marketplace features vetted models with performance benchmarks, safety ratings, and deployment guides.
            </p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl shadow bg-primary" data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-delay="300">
          <dt class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-white md:text-xl">
